163
00:10:46,128 --> 00:10:50,866
{\an1}They don't allow dogs
here, so I used Man-Beast
Transformation to get him in.

164
00:10:53,735 --> 00:10:56,771
Argh!

165
00:10:56,804 --> 00:11:00,606
Yoooow!!!

166
00:11:00,641 --> 00:11:02,274
Ahhhhh!

167
00:11:06,745 --> 00:11:09,179
[whine]

168
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:25,893
Got a strike!!

169
00:11:25,926 --> 00:11:26,693
Or something...

170
00:11:31,263 --> 00:11:33,164
Hey, watch it,
would you, Choji!?

171
00:11:33,197 --> 00:11:34,767
{\an1}The water level dropped!

172
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,001
{\an1}Ugh, just great.
Now what...

173
00:11:37,035 --> 00:11:39,236
{\an1}<i>(Neji)</i>
<i>How can we soak</i>
<i>with no water!?</i>

174
00:11:39,269 --> 00:11:40,804
They're being
so noisy!

175
00:11:40,837 --> 00:11:42,438
{\an1}<i>(Choji) </i>
<i>Sorry, guys...</i>

176
00:11:42,471 --> 00:11:46,274
{\an1}I'm really surprised you were
able to meet us here. Your
mother is usually so strict.

177
00:11:46,307 --> 00:11:47,943
Yeah, she's
such a pain...

178
00:11:47,977 --> 00:11:50,979
{\an1}My mom always piled
on the chores when
I'm off, too...

179
00:11:51,012 --> 00:11:54,213
{\an1}If I complain, my
dad says, "Mind
Destruction Jutsu..!"

180
00:11:54,247 --> 00:11:55,015
[gasps]

181
00:11:56,716 --> 00:11:59,619
But, I am a
bit jealous...

182
00:11:59,652 --> 00:12:00,719
{\an1}What!?

183
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:06,091
Choji, use your
Expansion Jutsu.

184
00:12:06,124 --> 00:12:07,692
Huh? What for?

185
00:12:07,725 --> 00:12:09,026
Just do it.

186
00:12:09,060 --> 00:12:10,660
Yeah, sure,
why not?

187
00:12:10,694 --> 00:12:12,662
Expansion Jutsu!

188
00:12:19,767 --> 00:12:23,336
Whoa, where'd all
this water come from?

189
00:12:23,370 --> 00:12:26,139
{\an1}Sure, there's more
water, but there's hardly
any room to move..!

190
00:12:26,173 --> 00:12:28,908
[laughing]

191
00:12:28,941 --> 00:12:33,410
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Man, I always have fun</i>
<i>with them! It's way</i>
<i>better than being alone!</i>

192
00:12:33,444 --> 00:12:36,613
{\an7}<i>I wonder what he's</i>
<i>doin' right now...</i>

193
00:12:39,282 --> 00:12:41,951
{\an7}<i>He's the only one</i>
<i>who's really changed...</i>

194
00:12:41,984 --> 00:12:44,619
{\an7}<i>If he hadn't, he'd</i>
<i>be here too...</i>

195
00:12:47,989 --> 00:12:50,925
Huh? Sasuke?
But, how..?

196
00:12:50,958 --> 00:12:53,326
Something wrong?

197
00:12:56,029 --> 00:13:00,331
{\an5}What's with that look,
Naruto? You're not
planning some kind of
mischief, are you..?

198
00:13:00,364 --> 00:13:04,135
{\an4}What are you talking
about, Neji? I was
just lost in thought,
that's all!

199
00:13:04,168 --> 00:13:07,671
{\an5}Well I hope that's
true! You'd better
not be up to your
old tricks again!

200
00:13:07,704 --> 00:13:09,739
{\an1}What!? What tricks?

201
00:13:09,772 --> 00:13:10,873
{\an1}Peeping, perhaps?

202
00:13:10,906 --> 00:13:12,208
Whaaat?

203
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,709
<i>[girls giggling]</i>

204
00:13:14,743 --> 00:13:17,745
{\an1}Oh, right. On the
other side is...

205
00:13:19,213 --> 00:13:22,682
{\an8}<i>There's a whole</i>
<i>different kind of</i>
<i>fun to be had...</i>

